reviewText: Well it's been a while since i've seen corey feldman in anything except in the newpaper or on extra promoting his new reality show..oh yes..his forgettable guest appearance on "Son of a beach", but his acting in this flick was not half bad and without spoiling anything in the film (you gotta watch it for yourself)he just chose the wrong project but i guess anything that comes his way right now is cool with him (don't quote me on that!) If your in too a b-grade light comedy that won't take away too much time in your life..why not go for it (for corey's sake of course!)Note: What's up with the $99,00 price tag!!!
Title: South Beach Academy VHS
